          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "# 🌱 VeriVerde Sustainability Insights\n\n## Energy & Environmental Monitoring\n\nThis dashboard provides real-time insights into your infrastructure's environmental impact and energy efficiency.\n\n### Key Metrics:\n- **Energy Consumption**: Real-time power usage in kilowatt-hours (kWh)\n- **Temperature Monitoring**: Server room/rack temperature for optimal cooling efficiency\n- **Renewable Energy**: Percentage of power from renewable sources\n- **CO₂ Emissions**: Estimated carbon footprint based on energy consumption\n- **Efficiency Score**: Overall operational efficiency (0-100)\n\n### Carbon Footprint Calculation\n**Formula**: `CO₂ (kg) = Energy (kWh) × CO₂ Factor (kg/kWh) × (1 - Renewable %)`\n\n**Default CO₂ Factor**: 0.233 kg/kWh (EU average 2024)\n\n### Best Practices:\n- Maintain temperature between 20-24°C for optimal efficiency\n- Monitor energy spikes during business hours\n- Track renewable energy percentage trends\n- Set alerts for high temperature or unusual energy consumption\n\n### Compliance:\n✅ Supports ESG reporting requirements  \n✅ Enables carbon footprint tracking for sustainability goals  \n✅ Provides data for green certifications and audits\n\n---\n**RHINOMETRIC VeriVerde** - Sustainability module for responsible IT operations",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
